```plantuml
@startuml usds_justice40-tool

actor User
participant "Client App (React)" as Client
participant "Data Pipeline (ETL)" as Pipeline
participant "Scoring Engine" as Scoring
participant "Map Tile Generator" as MapGen
database "S3 Data Lake" as S3

User -> Client: Interacts with map/interface
Client -> Pipeline: Requests data (API call)
Pipeline -> S3: Retrieves raw datasets
S3 --> Pipeline: Returns raw data
Pipeline -> Pipeline: Transforms data (ETL)
Pipeline -> S3: Stores processed data
Pipeline --> Client: Returns processed data

Client -> Scoring: Requests community scores
Scoring -> S3: Retrieves processed data
S3 --> Scoring: Returns processed data
Scoring -> Scoring: Calculates scores
Scoring -> S3: Stores score results
Scoring --> Client: Returns score results

Client -> MapGen: Requests map tiles
MapGen -> S3: Retrieves GeoJSON data
S3 --> MapGen: Returns spatial data
MapGen -> MapGen: Generates vector tiles
MapGen --> Client: Returns map tiles

Client -> Client: Renders UI with data/scores/tiles
@enduml
```